Subject: Migrate from aws to gcp
Description: Currently our EPP is hosted in aws and it needs to be migrated to GCP environment. Need your technical team assistance for the migration process.
Solution_Comment__c:
I have changed the value for the parameter support_syslogng from 0 to 1 inside the mysql, and saved the configuration in the UI again.
After that the logs were received in the SIEM servers.
Customer confirmed that the ticket can be closed.
